CAPSTONE PROJECT — Multi-Cloud Enterprise Architecture

⭐ HOW WE WILL PRACTICE EACH SCENARIO

For every scenario, you will get:

✅ 1. Real-time Story

(e.g., “Your company wants to move to multi-cloud for DR…”)

✅ 2. Architecture Explanation

Differences between AWS / Azure / GCP.

✅ 3. Step-By-Step Console Guide

Each cloud separately.

✅ 4. CLI Commands

AWS CLI

Azure CLI

gcloud

PowerShell versions for all

✅ 5. Troubleshooting

Real production issues explained.

✅ 6. Verification Tests

Ping tests / curl tests / logs / metrics.

✅ 7. Assignments

You will do them and confirm before we move to the next scenario.